Metadata.dc:title: Home of the Canoo WebTest Distribution Site
Metadata.description: Canoo WebTest is a free open source tool for automated testing of web applications. It calls web pages and verifies the results, giving comprehensive reports on success and failure. The WhitePaper gives an overview of the features and the design rationale. Detailed information is provided in the Syntax Reference and the Installation and Troubleshooting guide.
